ActCanadian Free Trade Agreement Implementation Act
SubjectOrder Designating the Minister of Public Safety and Emergency Preparedness as the Minister for the Purposes of the Canadian Free Trade Agreement Implementation Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2022-25 of January 13, 2022; and (2) designating the Minister of PUBLIC SAFETY AND EMERGENCY PREPAREDNESS, a member of the King’s Privy Council for Canada, as the Minister for the purposes of the CANADIAN FREE TRADE AGREEMENT IMPLEMENTATION ACT.
